Uses of Package
net.objectzoo.ebc.builder

  • Packages that use net.objectzoo.ebc.builder 
    Package Description
    net.objectzoo.ebc.builder
    This package contains an internal flow builder DSL implementation that can be used to combine EBCs to flows
  • Classes in net.objectzoo.ebc.builder used by net.objectzoo.ebc.builder 
    Class Description
    NewFlowConnector
    This class contains some static methods used to continue a DSL sentence with a new flow of EBCs
    SendsResultConnector
    Instances of this class allow the DSL like definition of EBC flows by attaching the next EBC to a flow that ended with a SendsResult or Event.
    SendsSignalConnector
    Instances of this class allow the DSL like definition of EBC flows by attaching the next EBC to a flow that ended with a SendsSignal or Event0.
